  <official_title>An Observational 20-year, Cross-sectional, Long-term Follow up of the Patient Cohort Enrolled in the Pivotal Study of BetaseronÂ® (Interferon Beta-1b) in Relapsing-remitting Multiple Sclerosis</official_title>
